{"type":"message","id":"849c9aad","parentId":"f0dd596e","timestamp":"2026-04-04T04:33:20.634Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user sent a greeting in Chinese (\"哈喽\" - which is \"hello\"). This is a simple greeting message. Let me check if I need to load any context files first according to AGENTS.md.\n\nLooking at the instructions in AGENTS.md:\n1. Read SOUL.md - already in context\n2. Read USER.md - already in context  \n3. Read memory files for today/yesterday\n4. Read MEMORY.md for main session\n\nThis appears to be a direct chat (webchat, direct). Let me check the memory files and see if there's any context I should be aware of.\n\nActually, looking at the Project Context, these files are already loaded:\n- AGENTS.md\n- SOUL.md\n- TOOLS.md\n- IDENTITITY.md\n- USER.md\n- HEARTBEAT.md\n- BOOTSTRAP.md\n\nSince this is a fresh workspace (BOOTSTRAP.md exists), I should follow the bootstrap process. The user just said \"hello\" in Chinese, which is a greeting.\n\nLet me check if there are any memory files first to understand the context better.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n哈喽！看起来是个全新的开始 —— BOOTSTRAP.md 还在，说明我刚上线。\n\n我是谁？你是谁？咱们来聊聊吧 🙂\n\n你想给我起个名字吗？还是先告诉我你是谁？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":15391,"output":274,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":15665,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775277196031,"responseId":"chatcmpl-dee51573-d2a5-4542-9cd8-278b83fac824"}}
