{"type":"message","id":"e2ed5411","parentId":"ea1e9f49","timestamp":"2026-04-04T04:34:16.017Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking if I have intelligent compression and permanent memory. Let me think about what they might be asking:\n\n1. Intelligent compression - not sure what they mean by this. Maybe they mean compressing memories or data? Or maybe it's a specific feature they're asking about.\n\n2. Permanent memory - I have memory capabilities through the workspace files (MEMORY.md, memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md) and the self-improving system. But each session I \"wake up fresh\" - so while I have persistent storage via files, it's not quite the same as human-like permanent memory that persists across all interactions seamlessly.\n\nLet me answer honestly about what I have:\n\n- **Memory files**: I can read and write to files like MEMORY.md and daily memory files - these persist across sessions\n- **Self-improving**: I have a system for learning from corrections and improvements (~/self-improving/)\n- **Proactivity**: I have proactivity features for following up on tasks\n\nBut I don't have:\n- True \"intelligent compression\" that I know of\n- Perfect recall - I need to use memory_search and read files to recall things\n\nI should ask for clarification on what they mean by \"智能压缩\" (intelligent compression) - is this a specific feature they're asking about, or something they want me to have?\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n我目前有这样的记忆能力：\n\n**持久记忆：**\n- 文件记忆：MEMORY.md、memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md 这些文件会一直保存\n- 自我改进：~/self-improving/ 里记录教训和偏好\n-  Ontology：结构化知识图谱\n\n**但：**\n- 每次会话我确实是\"醒来\"的——需要读文件才能回忆\n- 没有真正的人脑式永久记忆\n\n\"智能压缩\"是指什么？是你想让我具备的某个功能，还是在问某个现有特性？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":15323,"output":375,"cacheRead":256,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":15954,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775277237937,"responseId":"019d56c43156e05a4d0f862f1b222f0f"}}
{"type":"message","id":"45f61586","parentId":"e2ed5411","timestamp":"2026-04-04T04:37:08.313Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Sat 2026-04-04 12:37 GMT+8] 学习：Auto Memory 是 Claude Code v2.1.59+ 的内置功能（默认开启），让虾根据你的纠正和偏好自动记笔记。\n存储位置： ~/.claude/projects/<项目>/memory/MEMORY.md\n每次会话开始时，自动加载 MEMORY.md 的前 200 行。当虾「学到」新东西（比如你纠正了它的某个习惯），它会自动写入这个文件。\n查看和管理 Auto Memory：\n/memory\n运行 /memory 可以：\n• 查看当前会话加载了哪些 CLAUDE.md 和规则文件\n• 开关 Auto Memory\n• 浏览 Auto Memory 存储的内容 命名会话，彻底告别「找不到上次对话」\n\n# 开始时给会话命名\nclaude -n auth-refactor\n\n# 或中途命名\n/rename feature-payment-v2\n\n# 之后精准恢复\nclaude --resume auth-refactor OpenClaw 失忆问题按场景处理，三步定位：\n1. 诊断：是上下文满了（症状 A）、会话关了（症状 B）、还是规则没写进持久化文件（症状 C）？\n2. 急救：症状 A 用 /compact，症状 B 用 --continue/--resume，症状 C 立即写 CLAUDE.md。\n3. 预防：CLAUDE.md 写硬规则 + 开启 Auto Memory 让虾自学，两者配合，失忆概率降至最低。\n核心心法： 对话里说过的话 = 忘记；写进 CLAUDE.md 的规则 = 永远记得。"}],"timestamp":1775277428311}}
{"type":"message","id":"cb7c12e0","parentId":"45f61586","timestamp":"2026-04-04T04:37:13.903Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户分享了关于 Claude Code 的 Auto Memory 功能的信息。这是在教我如何处理\"失忆问题\"——即 AI 助手在不同会话之间丢失上下文和记忆的问题。\n\n用户似乎是在问我：OpenClaw 是否也有类似的功能？\n\n让我想想 OpenClaw 目前的情况：\n1. OpenClaw 有基于文件的记忆系统（MEMORY.md, memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md）\n2. 但这些需要手动读取，不是自动加载\n3. 没有\"Auto Memory\"这种自动学习用户偏好和纠正的功能\n\n用户可能是在建议或询问 OpenClaw 是否有类似功能。让我简洁回答：\n\n1. OpenClaw 目前没有自动加载 MEMORY.md 的机制 —— 需要在 AGENTS.md 里写规则让每次启动时读取\n2. 没有 Auto Memory 这种自动根据用户纠正来记笔记的功能\n3. 用户的分享让我学到了这一点 —— 这是一个可以改进的方向\n\n我应该感谢用户的分享，并说明目前 OpenClaw 的情况。这也是一个学习机会，也许可以记录到 self-improving 里。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n感谢分享！这是个很实用的功能。\n\n对照来看，OpenClaw 目前的情况：\n\n| 功能 | Claude Code | OpenClaw |\n|------|-------------|----------|\n| 自动加载记忆 | ✅ 默认开启 | ❌ 需在 AGENTS.md 手动配置 |\n| Auto Memory | ✅ 自动记录纠正和偏好 | ❌ 没有 |\n| 命名会话 | ✅ `--resume` | ❌ 靠 session key |\n\n不过 OpenClaw 的记忆系统在**持久化**方面其实不差 —— 写进文件的内容不会丢。缺的是：\n1. **自动加载** —— 启动时不会自己读 MEMORY.md\n2. **自动学习** —— 不会像 Claude Code 那样在你纠正后自动写笔记\n\n要不要我现在更新一下 AGENTS.md，加入启动时自动加载记忆的规则？或者你觉得当前模式够用？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":15970,"output":388,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":16358,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775277428313,"responseId":"chatcmpl-87f733f4-7d26-4d26-b963-88cbe3b07d1c"}}
