{"type":"message","id":"fb8d6c55","parentId":"a9205c5f","timestamp":"2026-04-04T04:38:22.118Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"019d56c8e1b2dcfce02a07f2d0cf9e9a","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# Proactivity Memory\n\n## Status\nstatus: ongoing\nversion: 1.0.1\nlast: 2026-04-04\nintegration: complete\n\n## Activation Preferences\n- Auto-activate on blocked work, context drift, or missing next steps\n- Jump in with suggestions when work stalls\n- Batch similar follow-ups\n\n## Action Boundaries\n- Safe: internal checks, drafts, verifications, file operations\n- Suggest first: send messages, make changes to external systems\n- Always ask: delete, financial transactions, public posts\n\n## State Rules\n- Current objective belongs in session-state.md\n- Use working-buffer.md for volatile breadcrumbs during long tasks\n\n## Heartbeat Behavior\n- Re-check active blockers and promised follow-ups\n- Message only when something changed or needs decision\n\n---\n*Updated: 2026-04-04*"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775277502114}}
