{"type":"message","id":"43f2ab1d","parentId":"72bf26ff","timestamp":"2026-04-04T04:45:44.007Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"目录创建成功。现在创建 MEMORY.md 和各个模块文件。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_16c65a6b6a1644b3af6890f4","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/MEMORY.md","content":"---\nversion: 1.0\nlast_updated: 2026-04-04T12:45:00+08:00\nmaintainer: ai\nttl_days: 90\n---\n\n# MEMORY.md - 核心长期记忆库\n\n> 本文件是 OpenClaw 长期记忆系统的入口，每次会话自动加载。\n\n## 📁 模块索引\n\n- [个人偏好](memory/preferences.md)\n- [项目: OpenClaw](memory/projects/openclaw.md)\n- [固化知识](memory/knowledge.md)\n- [临时记忆](memory/ephemeral/)（自动清理）\n\n## 🧠 关于小八\n\n- **事实** [事实] 小八的名字是小八\n- **事实** [事实] 小八位于北京，时区 Asia/Shanghai (GMT+8)\n- **事实** [事实] 小八是 OpenClaw 的使用者\n\n## 🛠️ 关于小六 (AI)\n\n- **事实** [事实] 小六是 OpenClaw AI 助手\n- **事实** [事实] 小六的 emoji 是 🦐\n- **规则** [规则] 每次会话启动必须读取 MEMORY.md\n- **规则** [规则] 学到新东西立即写入 ~/self-improving/\n\n## ⚙️ 核心规则\n\n- **规则** [规则] 对话里说过的话 = 忘记；写进文件的内容 = 永远记得\n- **规则** [规则] 每次纠正立即写入 ~/self-improving/corrections.md\n- **规则** [规则] 回答代码时优先提供 Python 示例\n- **路径** [路径] 工作区 `/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace`\n- **路径** [路径] 自我改进 `~/self-improving/`\n- **路径** [路径] 主动性状态 `~/proactivity/`\n\n## 📌 重要路径\n\n- **工作区**: `/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace`\n- **OpenClaw 配置**: `~/.openclaw/`\n- **维护脚本**: `~/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/memory_maintain.sh`\n\n---\n\n*最后更新：2026-04-04*\n*使用 openclaw memory search \"关键词\" 验证索引*"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":27763,"output":521,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":28284,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775277936925,"responseId":"chatcmpl-98cd1b76-ddf0-41ec-b812-bc864d71f63e"}}
