{"type":"message","id":"6bb8837a","parentId":"aaa7310a","timestamp":"2026-04-04T04:46:09.703Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"继续创建其他模块文件。\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019d56cf418d39fe295fc84fe7cf31fa","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# 项目: OpenClaw\n\n> OpenClaw AI 助手配置和知识\n\n## 基本信息\n\n- **路径**: `/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace`\n- **配置**: `~/.openclaw/openclaw.json`\n- **模型**: codingplan/minimax-m2.5\n- **时区**: Asia/Shanghai\n\n## 记忆系统\n\n- 核心文件: `MEMORY.md`\n- 每日日志: `memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md`\n- 自我改进: `~/self-improving/`\n- 主动性: `~/proactivity/`\n\n## 已安装技能\n\n- feishu-doc / feishu-drive / feishu-wiki / feishu-perm (飞书)\n- coding-agent (编码代理)\n- gh-issues (GitHub issues)\n- healthcheck (安全检查)\n- session-logs (会话日志)\n- summarize (总结)\n- weather (天气)\n- ...更多见 skills/ 目录\n\n## 常见命令\n\n```bash\nopenclaw gateway status    # 网关状态\nopenclaw gateway restart   # 重启网关\nopenclaw plugins list      # 插件列表\n```\n\n---\n\n*最后更新：2026-04-04*","path":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/memory/projects/openclaw.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":8632,"output":305,"cacheRead":19968,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":28905,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775277946689,"responseId":"019d56cf30c0eacc449094eb701d2e14"}}
