{"type":"message","id":"3b29ebd0","parentId":"594160f6","timestamp":"2026-04-04T04:46:25.936Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"继续创建 knowledge 和 ephemeral。\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019d56d01927072dd6f8cf767bf9e579","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# 固化知识\n\n> 长期积累不会改变的知识\n\n## 技术栈\n\n- [知识] OpenClaw 基于 Node.js v22.22.1\n- [知识] 默认 shell 是 bash\n- [知识] 运行在 WSL2 (Linux 6.6.87.2-microsoft-standard-WSL2)\n\n## 记忆系统架构\n\n- [知识] 会话记忆 = 内存临时缓存（会话结束即清空）\n- [知识] 每日日志 = memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md（需主动调用）\n- [知识] 长期记忆 = MEMORY.md（每次会话自动加载）\n\n## 插件系统\n\n- [知识] memory-core = 默认内存插件\n- [知识] 插件槽位在 openclaw.json 的 plugins.slots\n\n---\n\n*最后更新：2026-04-04*","path":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/memory/knowledge.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":1936,"output":228,"cacheRead":27008,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":29172,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775277969714,"responseId":"019d56d00ece325ba273a30eb2083cc5"}}
