{"type":"message","id":"6ff9d5fa","parentId":"e003f348","timestamp":"2026-04-04T04:52:03.641Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The OpenClaw plugins architecture seems different than expected. Let me write a guide for installing LanceDB when the user has CLI access.\n\nBut looking back at the instructions the user shared earlier, it mentioned:\n```\nbash\n# 安装插件\nopenclaw plugins install @openclaw/memory-lancedb\n\n# 修改配置文件 ~/.openclaw/openclaw.json\n# 在 plugins 部分添加以下配置，将 memory-lancedb 指定为记忆槽位\n{\n \"plugins\": {\n \"slots\": {\n \"memory\": \"@openclaw/memory-lancedb\" \n }\n }\n}\n\n# 重启 Gateway 使配置生效\nopenclaw gateway restart\n```\n\nLet me create a guide document for this.\n\nFor now, let me provide the summary of what was done and what remains.\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019d56d49129ffc50e5e19dde7dd307e","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# LanceDB 插件安装指南\n\n> 升级记忆检索性能从默认的 SQLite 到向量数据库\n\n## 当前状态\n\n- **当前插件**: memory-core (默认 SQLite)\n- **升级目标**: LanceDB (向量检索)\n\n## 安装步骤\n\n### 1. 安装插件\n\n```bash\nopenclaw plugins install @openclaw/memory-lancedb\n```\n\n### 2. 修改配置\n\n编辑 `~/.openclaw/openclaw.json`:\n\n```json\n{\n  \"plugins\": {\n    \"slots\": {\n      \"memory\": \"@openclaw/memory-lancedb\"\n    }\n  }\n}\n```\n\n### 3. 重启 Gateway\n\n```bash\nopenclaw gateway restart\n```\n\n### 4. 验证\n\n```bash\nopenclaw plugins info\n# 或\nopenclaw memory search \"测试关键词\"\n```\n\n## 预期效果\n\n- 更快的语义检索\n- 支持向量相似度搜索\n- 适合大规模知识库\n\n## 回退\n\n如需回退, 修改配置 `\"memory\": \"@openclaw/memory-core\"` 并重启即可。\n\n---\n\n*文档创建: 2026-04-04*\n*需手动执行, 因为当前环境无 openclaw CLI*","path":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/memory/LANCEDB_INSTALL.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":1675,"output":446,"cacheRead":35840,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":37961,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"s