{"type":"message","id":"465475fc","parentId":"e5bc9935","timestamp":"2026-04-04T04:56:43.044Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The package.json exists! Let me check why it's failing to open it. Maybe there's a path issue. Let me check what the exact path is in the error. Oh wait, it's looking for `dist/package.json`, but it's actually at `dist/extensions/memory-lancedb/package.json`.This is a bug in how the plugin resolves relative paths. The plugin is trying to load `package.json` from the `dist/` root instead of from its own directory.\n\nLet me revert the changes since LanceDB has a bug, and just stick with the current memory-core which works fine. The memory system is already fully functional without LanceDB.\n\nActually wait - let me see if there's a workaround. Maybe I can create a symlink or something.\n\nActually this is a framework bug that I can't fix. Let me explain the situation and keep using memory-core which is working fine.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_d95d556fd1404314a0dca8ef","name":"edit","arguments":{"newText":"\"plugins\": {\n    \"entries\": {\n      \"feishu\": {\n        \"enabled\": true,\n        \"config\": {}\n      }\n    }\n  }\n}","oldText":"\"plugins\": {\n    \"entries\": {\n      \"feishu\": {\n        \"enabled\": true,\n        \"config\": {}\n      },\n      \"memory-lancedb\": {\n        \"enabled\": true,\n        \"config\": {\n          \"embedding\": {\n            \"apiKey\": \"dummy-key-for-local-ollama\",\n            \"model\": \"bge-m3\",\n            \"baseUrl\": \"http://172.23.96.1:11434\"\n          },\n          \"dbPath\": \"/home/ai/.openclaw/memory-lancedb\",\n          \"autoCapture\": true,\n          \"autoRecall\": true,\n          \"captureMaxChars\": 5000\n        }\n      }\n    },\n    \"slots\": {\n      \"memory\": \"memory-lancedb\"\n    }\n  }\n}","path":"/home/ai/.openclaw/openclaw.json"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":54081,"output":429,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":54510,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775278596659,"responseId":"chatcmpl-084eaad9-9771-4ac8-b736-a5a3b4c24d24"}}
