{"type":"message","id":"5c046540","parentId":"27bc5afa","timestamp":"2026-04-04T04:56:46.619Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now let me explain to the user what happened.\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n## 结果\n\n**LanceDB 插件无法启用** — 这是一个框架级 bug：\n\n```\nError: ENOENT: no such file or directory, open \n'/home/ai/.nvm/versions/node/v22.22.1/lib/node_modules/openclaw/dist/package.json'\n```\n\n插件内部的路径解析有问题，需要修复 OpenClaw 本身。\n\n---\n\n**不过没关系！** 当前系统已经很完善：\n\n| 组件 | 状态 |\n|------|------|\n| memory-core (SQLite) | ✅ 正常工作 |\n| MEMORY.md 模块化 | ✅ 已建立 |\n| 维护脚本 | ✅ 已完成 |\n| Cron 定时任务 | ✅ 已配置 |\n| Memory Keeper | ✅ 已完成 |\n\n**向量搜索 vs 关键词搜索：**\n- memory-core 用 **SQLite 全文搜索** — 够用\n- LanceDB 用 **向量嵌入搜索** — 更快更准，但目前有 bug\n\n等官方修复后可以再尝试升级。当前记忆系统已经完全可用了！\n\n要不要我更新文档记录这个情况？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":54542,"output":225,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":54767,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775278603058,"responseId":"chatcmpl-96a4eb59-514a-440f-ba37-86abb87d88cc"}}
