{"type":"message","id":"6e2241e9","parentId":"26feacda","timestamp":"2026-04-04T04:58:57.435Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"小八让我自己更新文档记录这个情况。我需要更新之前创建的 LANCEDB_INSTALL.md 文件，说明当前无法安装的原因和状态。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_da5907f14cfa46ddaa9ce47b","name":"edit","arguments":{"oldText":"# LanceDB 插件安装指南\n\n> 升级记忆检索性能从默认的 SQLite 到向量数据库\n\n## 当前状态\n\n- **当前插件**: memory-core (默认 SQLite)\n- **升级目标**: LanceDB (向量检索)\n\n## 安装步骤\n\n### 1. 安装插件\n\n```bash\nopenclaw plugins install @openclaw/memory-lancedb\n```\n\n### 2. 修改配置\n\n编辑 `~/.openclaw/openclaw.json`:\n\n```json\n{\n  \"plugins\": {\n    \"slots\": {\n      \"memory\": \"@openclaw/memory-lancedb\"\n    }\n  }\n}\n```\n\n### 3. 重启 Gateway\n\n```bash\nopenclaw gateway restart\n```\n\n### 4. 验证\n\n```bash\nopenclaw plugins info\n# 或\nopenclaw memory search \"测试关键词\"\n```\n\n## 预期效果\n\n- 更快的语义检索\n- 支持向量相似度搜索\n- 适合大规模知识库\n\n## 回退\n\n如需回退, 修改配置 `\"memory\": \"@openclaw/memory-core\"` 并重启即可。\n\n---\n\n*文档创建: 2026-04-04*\n*需手动执行, 因为当前环境无 openclaw CLI*","newText":"# LanceDB 插件安装指南\n\n> 升级记忆检索性能从默认的 SQLite 到向量数据库\n\n## 当前状态 (2026-04-04)\n\n- **当前插件**: memory-core (默认 SQLite) ✅ 正常工作\n- **升级目标**: LanceDB (向量检索) ❌ 暂不可用\n\n### 已知问题\n\nLanceDB 插件加载失败，报错：\n```\nError: ENOENT: no such file or directory, open \n'/home/ai/.nvm/versions/node/v22.22.1/lib/node_modules/openclaw/dist/package.json'\n```\n\n这是 OpenClaw 框架级 bug，插件内部路径解析问题。\n\n### 尝试过的方案\n\n1. 配置 embedding 使用本地 Ollama 的 bge-m3 模型 ✅ 可行\n2. 添加 plugins.slots.memory 指向 memory-lancedb ❌ 仍报错\n3. 启用后 doctor 检查显示 plugin 加载失败\n\n## 安装步骤 (待框架修复后使用)\n\n### 1. 确保有 embedding API\n\n**方案A: OpenAI (付费)**\n```json\n{\n  \"embedding\": {\n    \"apiKey\": \"env:OPENAI_API_KEY\",\n    \"model\": \"text-embedding-3-small\"\n  }\n}\n```\n\n**方案B: 本地 Ollama (免费)**\n```json\n{\n  \"embedding\": {\n    \"apiKey\": \"dummy-key-for-local-ollama\",\n    \"model\": \"bge-m3\",\n    \"baseUrl\": \"http://172.23.96.1:11434\"\n  }\n}\n```\n> 注：本地需要先安装 bge-m3 模型：`ollama pull bge-m3`\n\n### 2. 修改配置\n\n编辑 `~/.openclaw/openclaw.json`:\n\n```json\n{\n  \"plugins\": {\n    \"entries\": {\n      \"memory-lancedb\": {\n        \"enabled\": true,\n        \"config\": {\n          \"embedding\": {\n            \"apiKey\": \"dummy-key-for-local-ollama\",\n            \"model\": \"bge-m3\",\n            \"baseUrl\": \"http://172.23.96.1:11434\"\n          },\n          \"dbPath\": \"/home/ai/.openclaw/memory-lancedb\",\n          \"autoCapture\": true,\n          \"autoRecall\": true,\n          \"captureMaxChars\": 5000\n        }\n      }\n    },\n    \"slots\": {\n      \"memory\": \"memory-lancedb\"\n    }\n  }\n}\n```\n\n### 3. 验证\n\n```bash\nopenclaw plugins doctor\n# 或\nopenclaw gateway restart && openclaw memory search \"测试\"\n```\n\n## 当前替代方案\n\nmemory-core (SQLite) 足够日常使用，支持：\n- 关键词搜索\n- 全文检索\n- 模块化 MEMORY.md 加载\n\n等到框架修复后再升级。\n\n---\n\n*最后更新: 2026-04-04*","path":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/memory/LANCEDB_INSTALL.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":53375,"output":935,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":54310,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775278720354,"responseId":"chatcmpl-ceed7b8a-aa10-4e65-b3f5-7d90f80780cc"}}
