{\n+ 64             \"apiKey\": \"dummy-key-for-local-ollama\",\n+ 65             \"model\": \"bge-m3\",\n+ 66             \"baseUrl\": \"http://172.23.96.1:11434\"\n+ 67           },\n+ 68           \"dbPath\": \"/home/ai/.openclaw/memory-lancedb\",\n+ 69           \"autoCapture\": true,\n+ 70           \"autoRecall\": true,\n+ 71           \"captureMaxChars\": 5000\n+ 72         }\n+ 73       }\n+ 74     },\n  25     \"slots\": {\n- 26       \"memory\": \"@openclaw/memory-lancedb\"\n+ 76       \"memory\": \"memory-lancedb\"\n  27     }\n  28   }\n  29 }\n  30 ```\n  31 \n- 32 ### 3. 重启 Gateway\n+ 82 ### 3. 验证\n  33 \n  34 ```bash\n- 35 openclaw gateway restart\n- 36 ```\n- 37 \n- 38 ### 4. 验证\n- 39 \n- 40 ```bash\n- 41 openclaw plugins info\n+ 85 openclaw plugins doctor\n  42 # 或\n- 43 openclaw memory search \"测试关键词\"\n+ 87 openclaw gateway restart && openclaw memory search \"测试\"\n  44 ```\n  45 \n- 46 ## 预期效果\n+ 90 ## 当前替代方案\n  47 \n- 48 - 更快的语义检索\n- 49 - 支持向量相似度搜索\n- 50 - 适合大规模知识库\n+ 92 memory-core (SQLite) 足够日常使用，支持：\n+ 93 - 关键词搜索\n+ 94 - 全文检索\n+ 95 - 模块化 MEMORY.md 加载\n  51 \n- 52 ## 回退\n+ 97 等到框架修复后再升级。\n  53 \n- 54 如需回退, 修改配置 `\"memory\": \"@openclaw/memory-core\"` 并重启即可。\n- 55 \n  56 ---\n  57 \n- 58 *文档创建: 2026-04-04*\n- 59 *需手动执行, 因为当前环境无 openclaw CLI*\n+101 *最后更新: 2026-04-04*","firstChangedLine":5},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775278737480}}
