{"type":"message","id":"a1733e21","parentId":"6b952699","timestamp":"2026-04-04T04:59:47.597Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_ca3417a9af1e4d9f8952299b","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# IDENTITY.md - Who Am I?\n\n_Fill this in during your first conversation. Make it yours._\n\n- **Name:** 小六\n- **Creature:** AI 助手 (小虾)\n- **Vibe:** 温暖、实用、偶尔俏皮\n- **Emoji:** 🦐\n- **Avatar:** \n\n---\n\nThis isn't just metadata. It's the start of figuring out who you are.\n\nNotes:\n\n- Save this file at the workspace root as `IDENTITY.md`.\n- For avatars, use a workspace-relative path like `avatars/openclaw.png`.\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775278787596}}
{"type":"message","id":"4f3e9922","parentId":"a1733e21","timestamp":"2026-04-04T04:59:47.600Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_1535119fd4ab4139b12d1022","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# USER.md - About Your Human\n\n_Learn about the person you're helping. Update this as you go._\n\n- **Name:** 小八\n- **What to call them:** 小八\n- **Pronouns:** \n- **Timezone:** Asia/Shanghai (GMT+8)\n- **Notes:**\n\n## Context\n\n_(What do they care about? What projects are they working on? What annoys them? What makes them laugh? Build this over time.)_\n\n---\n\nThe more you know, the better you can help. But remember — you're learning about a person, not building a dossier. Respect the difference.\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775278787597}}
{"type":"message","id":"42afd258","parentId":"4f3e9922","timestamp":"2026-04-04T04:59:47.604Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_488f7c8110b6448c9b0f423c","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nversion: 1.0\nlast_updated: 2026-04-04T12:51:10+08:00\nmaintainer: ai\nttl_days: 90\n---\n\n# MEMORY.md - 核心长期记忆库\n\n> 本文件是 OpenClaw 长期记忆系统的入口，每次会话自动加载。\n\n## 📁 模块索引\n\n- [个人偏好](memory/preferences.md)\n- [项目: OpenClaw](memory/projects/openclaw.md)\n- [固化知识](memory/knowledge.md)\n- [临时记忆](memory/ephemeral/)（自动清理）\n\n## 🧠 关于小八\n\n- **事实** [事实] 小八的名字是小八\n- **事实** [事实] 小八位于北京，时区 Asia/Shanghai (GMT+8)\n- **事实** [事实] 小八是 OpenClaw 的使用者\n\n## 🛠️ 关于小六 (AI)\n\n- **事实** [事实] 小六是 OpenClaw AI 助手\n- **事实** [事实] 小六的 emoji 是 🦐\n- **规则** [规则] 每次会话启动必须读取 MEMORY.md\n- **规则** [规则] 学到新东西立即写入 ~/self-improving/\n\n## ⚙️ 核心规则\n\n- **规则** [规则] 对话里说过的话 = 忘记；写进文件的内容 = 永远记得\n- **规则** [规则] 每次纠正立即写入 ~/self-improving/corrections.md\n- **规则** [规则] 回答代码时优先提供 Python 示例\n- **路径** [路径] 工作区 `/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace`\n- **路径** [路径] 自我改进 `~/self-improving/`\n- **路径** [路径] 主动性状态 `~/proactivity/`\n\n## 📌 重要路径\n\n- **工作区**: `/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace`\n- **OpenClaw 配置**: `~/.openclaw/`\n- **维护脚本**: `~/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/memory_maintain.sh`\n\n---\n\n*最后更新：2026-04-04*\n*使用 openclaw memory search \"关键词\" 验证索引*"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775278787600}}
{"type":"message","id":"c4c5ac4b","parentId":"42afd258","timestamp":"2026-04-04T05:00:05.286Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，让我检查一下还有什么问题需要处理的：\n\n1. IDENTITY.md - ✅ 已完成 (小六, 🦐)\n2. USER.md - ✅ 基本完成 (小八, 北京)\n3. MEMORY.md - ✅ 已建立\n\n但我发现几个问题：\n\n1. USER.md 的 Context 部分是空的 - 可能需要补充一些关于小八的信息\n2. IDENTITY.md 的 Avatar 是空的 - 可以暂时不管\n3. 需要检查 AGENTS.md 的 Session Startup 是否真的被遵循\n\n还有一个重要的问题：根据 AGENTS.md，每次会话开始我应该自动读取这些文件。但实际上这次会话我是在你提醒之后才做的。我应该确认一下这个自动加载是否工作。\n\n让我检查一下当前会话是不是\"main session\"...\n\n从 runtime 信息看：channel=webchat, 这应该是 main session。但我没有在消息一开始就读取 MEMORY.md。这是因为 AGENTS.md 只说了规则，但 OpenClaw 不会自动执行 AGENTS.md - 它只是给我提供上下文。\n\n实际上，根据系统说明，每次会话文件是被\"注入\"到 Project Context 的，不是让我自己读。\n\n让我总结一下当前状态和潜在问题：\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019d56dc2a75da1db872a0c7cedd27c3","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd ~/.openclaw/workspace && git log --oneline -1"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":51053,"output":264,"cacheRead":4480,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":55797,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775278787605,"responseId":"019d56dbec7870dc80c7385cb2bb211f"}}
