{"type":"message","id":"2ae5972e","parentId":"45226f1f","timestamp":"2026-04-04T05:01:28.348Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"小八在问我是否自动写入新东西到记忆文件。\n\n让我检查当前的自我改进系统是否真的在工作。根据之前的 AGENTS.md 更新，我添加了 Auto Memory 规则，但实际上还没有真正被触发过。\n\n让我检查：\n1. ~/self-improving/corrections.md - 是否有内容？\n2. ~/self-improving/memory.md - 是否有内容？\n\n以及检查我是否真的在每次学到新东西时自动写入。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019d56de07510908d3bc5adda991c02b","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"~/self-improving/corrections.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019d56de0d9983219f95f48d76be2a11","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"~/self-improving/memory.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":1315,"output":144,"cacheRead":54528,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":55987,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775278870479,"responseId":"019d56ddce3bd7113589c1f54f93569c"}}
{"type":"message","id":"849a022e","parentId":"2ae5972e","timestamp":"2026-04-04T05:01:28.364Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"019d56de07510908d3bc5adda991c02b","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# Corrections Log\n\n<!-- Format:\n## YYYY-MM-DD\n- [HH:MM] Changed X → Y\n  Type: format|technical|communication|project\n  Context: where correction happened\n  Confirmed: pending (N/3) | yes | no\n-->"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775278888361}}
{"type":"message","id":"4aa4b400","parentId":"849a022e","timestamp":"2026-04-04T05:01:28.368Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"019d56de0d9983219f95f48d76be2a11","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# Self-Improving Memory\n\n## Confirmed Preferences\n<!-- Patterns confirmed by user, never decay -->\n\n## Active Patterns\n<!-- Patterns observed 3+ times, subject to decay -->\n\n## Recent (last 7 days)\n<!-- New corrections pending confirmation -->\n\n## 2026-04-04 - 长期记忆系统 (From 小八)\n\n### 核心概念\n- **MEMORY.md** = 长期记忆核心文件，每次会话自动加载\n- 文件即记忆：写进去的内容 = 永远记得\n- 三步流程：输入(你写) → 处理(AI读) → 维护(自动化)\n\n### 记忆层级\n| 层级 | 类比 | 存储位置 | 特点 |\n|------|------|----------|------|\n| 会话记忆 | 工作记忆 | 内存缓存 | 临时，会话结束即清空 |\n| 每日日志 | 短期日记 | memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md | 可跨会话，需主动调用 |\n| 长期记忆 | 核心知识库 | MEMORY.md | 每次会话自动加载，防失忆核心 |\n\n### 记忆插件\n- **memory-core**: 默认，开箱即用，够用\n- **LanceDB**: 专业版，更快更准的语义检索\n\n### 自动化 (可选)\n- 用 cron 定期从 daily log 提取信息更新到 MEMORY.md\n- 脚本示例：`~/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/update_memory.sh`\n\n### 验证方法\n```bash\nopenclaw gateway restart --debug\n# 观察日志中 memory_search 调用\nopenclaw plugins info\n```\n\n### 鲁棒性规范 (2026-04-04 小八)\n1. **YAML Frontmatter** - 头部加元数据\n```yaml\n---\nversion: 1.0\nlast_updated: 2026-04-04\nmaintainer: ai\nttl_days: 90\n---\n```\n\n2. **模块化拆分** - 避免单一文件\n```\n~/.openclaw/workspace/\n├── MEMORY.md          # 入口索引\n└── memory/\n    ├── preferences.md # 个人偏好\n    ├── projects/      # 按项目拆分\n    │   └── openclaw.md\n    ├── knowledge/     # 固化知识\n    └── ephemeral/     # 临时记忆（自动清理）\n```\n\n3. **语义标记** - 每条信息明确类型\n- **事实**：[事实] 我的默认时区是 Asia/Shanghai\n- **规则**：[规则] 回答代码时优先提供 Python 示例\n- **偏好**：[偏好] 避免使用 emoji\n- **路径**：[路径] 工作目录 `/home/ai/projects/main`\n- 带过期标记：[临时] xxx [expires: 2026-05-01]\n\n4. **自动化维护** - `~/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/memory_maintain.sh`\n   - 每日备份\n   - 检查过期条目\n   - Markdown 格式校验\n   - 去重\n\n5. **验证命令**\n```bash\nopenclaw memory list      # 列出已加载记忆\nopenclaw memory search \"关键词\"  # 搜索\nopenclaw memory rebuild   # 重建索引\n```\n\n6. **额外保护**\n   - git 版本控制\n   - flock 防并发冲突\n   - TTL 清理\n\n7. **AI Agent 维护** - Memory Keeper Agent\n   - 定期合并重复、删除过期、整理记忆\n\n---\n\n### 实施记录 (2026-04-04)\n\n✅ **已完成**:\n1. 创建 MEMORY.md (YAML frontmatter + 模块索引)\n2. 创建 memory/modules 目录结构:\n   - memory/preferences.md (个人偏好)\n   - memory/projects/openclaw.md (项目知识)\n   - memory/knowledge.md (固化知识)\n   - memory/ephemeral/ (临时记忆)\n3. 创建维护脚本 scripts/memory_maintain.sh (备份+过期检查+统计)\n4. Git 版本控制已配置\n5. .gitignore 已配置\n6. 首次备份已创建"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775278888364}}
{"type":"message","id":"dad89882","parentId":"4aa4b400","timestamp":"2026-04-04T05:01:54.754Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"现在回答小八的问题：目前还不是完全自动的。实际上：1. 我确实把今天学的知识写入了 ~/self-improving/memory.md（手动写入的）\n2. corrections.md 是空的 - 因为今天你没有纠正我任何东西\n\n问题是：AGENTS.md 里虽然写了规则\"自动写入\"，但 OpenClaw 本身没有 Claude Code 那种真正的 Auto Memory hooks。我现在的\"自动\"是指：我记得这个规则，主动去写。但不是框架级的自动触发。\n\n让我诚实地告诉小八。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n不完全是。实际情况：\n\n| 机制 | 状态 |\n|------|------|\n| AGENTS.md 规则 | ✅ 已写好 |\n| 手动写入知识 | ✅ 今天学的已写入 |\n| 纠正时自动写入 | ❌ 还没触发（今天没纠正） |\n| 框架级 Hook | ❌ OpenClaw 没有 Claude Code 那样的 Auto Memory hooks |\n\n**现在的工作方式：**\n- 我记得规则 → 主动去写\n- 今天你教我的东西，我是手动写入 `~/self-improving/memory.md` 的\n\n**理想的 Auto Memory（像 Claude Code）：**\n- 你纠正我一句话 → 框架自动捕获 → 写入文件\n\n**差距：**\nOpenClaw 缺一个 self-improvement hook。目前只能靠我\"记得规则后主动写\"。\n\n---\n\n要不要我把这个\"待实现\"记下来？以后可以实现框架级的自动记忆。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":52418,"output":291,"cacheRead":4480,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":57189,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775278888369,"responseId":"019d56dd75ec374a659acb09ce61daa3"}}
