{"type":"message","id":"36314f1c","parentId":"a71b0d9e","timestamp":"2026-04-04T05:14:54.846Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"完成了。现在总结一下给用户。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n## ✅ 改进完成！\n\n### 新增功能\n\n**Memory Keeper 增强版** 现在会：\n\n| 功能 | 说明 |\n|------|------|\n| 扫描记忆文件 | ✅ 原有 |\n| 检查过期条目 | ✅ 原有 |\n| ✅ **从 session 提取知识** | **新功能** |\n| ✅ **写入 ephemeral/** | **新功能** |\n| 更新 MEMORY.md | ✅ 原有 |\n\n### 工作流程\n\n```\n归档 Session (近3天)\n        ↓\n   Memory Keeper 扫描\n        ↓\n   提取含关键词的对话:\n   - \"记住\"\n   - \"学会\"\n   - \"偏好\"\n   - \"规则\"\n   - \"喜欢/讨厌\"\n        ↓\n   写入 memory/ephemeral/session_extract_日期.md\n        ↓\n   [可选] 手动 review 后合并到主记忆\n```\n\n### 运行结果\n\n```\n📊 总结：\n   - 过期条目: 0\n   - 临时文件: 0\n   - Session 提取: 执行成功（当前无历史 session）\n```\n\n**注意：** 当前测试环境没有历史 session 文件，所以没提取到内容。等运行一段时间后，每次 Keeper 运行会自动扫描并提取有价值的信息。\n\ncron 任务会在明早 04:00 自动运行增强版 Keeper ✓"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":5771,"output":278,"cacheRead":103424,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":109473,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775279672419,"responseId":"019d56ea0b01c02a23afc144962220a0"}}
